      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "rationale": "The CFD solver (ANSYS Fluent 2023R1) is a commercially validated, FDA-recognized simulation software with documented QA processes including version-controlled releases, regression test suites, and ISO 9001 certification. Internal SQA procedures include build verification, user access controls, and audit trails for all simulation runs.",
