      "rationale": "Validation activities used the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump geometry — the same device class and geometric archetype as the COU device. Operating conditions span the COU envelope (2–6 L/min, 2000–3500 RPM). Blood analog fluid properties match COU conditions. The validation domain is directly representative of the COU, with no extrapolation beyond validated operating range.",
      "acceptanceCriteria": {
        "id": "https://uofa.net/morrison/ac/validation-relevance",
        "type": "AcceptanceCriteria",
