      "rationale": "At Model Risk Level 2 for this COU, numerical solver error beyond code verification and discretization error assessment is not required. The commercial solver's iterative convergence is monitored via residual tracking (all residuals < 1e-5) and mass balance closure (< 0.01%). No additional solver error quantification is mandated at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 4."
    },
    {
