      "factorType": "Use error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "rationale": "Use error assessment is not required at Model Risk Level 2 for this COU. Simulation runs are performed by trained analysts following documented simulation procedures (SOP-CFD-2023-003). Peer review of setup files and boundary conditions is performed prior to each production run. Formal use error analysis is reserved for MRL 3 and above per ASME V&V 40 Table 4."
