      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "rationale": "Formal model form uncertainty quantification is not required at Model Risk Level 2. The k-omega SST turbulence model with non-Newtonian viscosity correction is selected based on published literature for blood pump CFD and FDA benchmark studies. Model form adequacy is implicitly addressed through the output comparison factor, where agreement within experimental uncertainty provides indirect evidence of model form sufficiency."
