      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "rationale": "Test sample characterization beyond what is documented in the FDA benchmark protocol is not required at Model Risk Level 2. The FDA benchmark provides sufficient sample documentation (pump geometry tolerances ±0.05 mm, surface finish Ra < 0.8 μm) for MRL 2 assessment. Statistical characterization of manufacturing variability across test samples is reserved for MRL 3."
